        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\n(1 comment)\n\nThis change should be made in the hibernate definitions (hbm.xml files) in so/mso-catalog-db/src/main/resources. Basically, you should change the hbm.xml file(s), then do an \"so\" build, which should regenerate MySQL-Catalog-schema.sql (under \"so\"). Then, copy the generated schema to docker-config/volumes/mariadb/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/db-sql-scripts/main-schemas.  Thanks.",
